settings.title: Wornstar Clothing
settings.content: Launched in a garage outside of Chicago in 2009, Wornstar Clothing has slowly grown into an underground rock n roll movement. Originally a side project of stylist and designer Sylvia Jensen and art director, designer and photographer Stephen Jensen, this husband and wife team sought to establish a brand to cater to their friends in the music industry. With their combined 50 years experience in the music industry they choose to follow their design instincts rather than what is on trend to create authentic rock n roll clothing.
